     Cold Contract is a turn-based tactic game with real-time strategy         
     elements.                                                                 
     You play a team leader, which has been left for dead by an unknown        
     man in a previous operation. Alive and blinded by his revenge, he         
     decides to hire a team of mercenaries to counter an operation of          
     the bad guy in a hostile region.                                          
                                                                               
     Most of parts of the game are generated from scratch for each new         
     game, including the regional map, the objectives, the list of             
     mercenaries and their equipment, the locations of enemies, the            
     location of each mission and much more!                                   
                                                                               
     Improve and develop your team, reinforce your squads, upgrade and         
     extend your options on the battlefield!                                   
                                                                               
     You must protect your positions against enemy assaults. Upgrade           
     your HQ to gain more power and new options. Improve your                  
     mercenaries with the gained experience during skirmishes. Select          
     the objectives according to your priority depending of the active         
     mission. There are eight missions available: rescue hostages,             
     destroy installations, VIP elimination are one of them.                   
                                                                               
     Several environments are available like villages, cities, military        
     bases, ... Most parts of the isometric environment are                    
     destructible, if you have enough firepower. You can open the door         
     or make your own door with a big hole in the wall. Use the                
     environment to vaporize enemies, to blind or poison them.                 
     Move with caution in deadly environment full of traps and mines!          
     Strike the enemy during day if your team is the best, or sneak in         
     the night to eliminate each target like a night wolf.                     
     features :                                                                
     Fully generated content for each new game (never fight on the same        
     maps, and team configuration)                                             
     Enhance the power of your mercenaries and the squads with twenty          
     levels of experience                                                      
     Seven skills, thirty perks, thirty equipment levels defining each         
     mercenaries                                                               
     Upgrade your tactical and strategical options with twenty-five            
     upgrades unlockable in your HQ                                            
     Real-time mechanics in order to manage your team and define your          
     objectives                                                                
     Turn-based battles in order to defeat the opposing force with             
     extended action points system and several tactical options                
     More than twenty five weapons from pistols to heavy machine guns          
     Several grenade versions and support material                             
     Old-school isometric maps fully destructible                              
     Reactive environment to bullets and explosives (for example hit a         
     gas cylinder and watch the fire burning your enemies)                     
     Several levels of behaviors for AI (rookies are unpredictables,           
     guards are careful, soldiers are dangerous, elite troops will be          
     your last nightmare)                                                      
     Day and night cycles influencing the behavior of your team and            
     enemies                                                                   
     Eight randomized missions appearing on enemy objectives                   
     Train militia in order to defend your positions                           
                                                                               
